<br>
So, for instance, you could type:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>/gu Hey, I just got a </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
then do NOT press enter yet. Instead, do the alt-left click thing on the item to bring up the item window, and click on the graphic. If it was something like &quot;A left goblin ear&quot;, then you would see your original typing down below now look like:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>/gu Hey, I just got a <br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:purple;">A left goblin ear</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->. Now just click for your cursor to be back in that line you type in, and press enter.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps!<br>
